00:04:42.500 --> 00:04:47.150 align:middle line:84%
This is village India,
with income over time

00:04:47.150 --> 00:04:48.320 align:middle line:90%
and over households.

00:04:48.320 --> 00:04:54.410 align:middle line:84%
And you may remember this
gradient, that in some sense,

00:04:54.410 --> 00:04:58.700 align:middle line:84%
