00:06:42.850 --> 00:06:43.570 align:middle line:90%
sharing.

00:06:43.570 --> 00:06:46.360 align:middle line:84%
Those lambdas are
correlated with things

00:06:46.360 --> 00:06:52.660 align:middle line:84%
like landholding, where the
value of the bull that they own

00:06:52.660 --> 00:06:57.350 align:middle line:84%
and plow with and the
